One thing to consider is that the notch in the pulley may not actually 
reflect top dead center. It may be in your best interest to verify this 
by turning the engine and watching the valves to find the true TDC, or 
by putting a dowl in a sparc plug hole. But then IANSD! (I Am Not Steve 
Dolan.) :)

